snippet.title: Bus Depot पर Bhelpuri बेचते हुए Spot किए गए Daya |CID |Latest Episode |Unlimited Action |20 Jan 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

In this intriguing case, the CID team delves into the abduction of the wife of a prominent and wealthy businessman. The kidnappers demand a peculiar ransom of 5 crores, to be delivered in 5 instalments at 5 different locations. As CID attempts to unravel this complex and strategic plot, they find themselves consistently outsmarted by the cunning perpetrators. Suspecting the involvement of an insider, CID faces the challenge of identifying the traitor within the businessman's circle. Watch this gripping episode to uncover the twists and turns in the pursuit of the kidnapper.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 948
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #cid2024  #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch more episodes of CID Best From TV :
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIUYuRlCxU2dJkUtocAxRIme

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Weather Update: दिल्ली से लेकर उत्तर भारत तक ठंड का सितम | जानें कैसा रहेगा मौसम | IMD | Hindi News
snippet.description:
Weather Update News: एक तरफ भीषण ठंड तो दूसरी तरफ घने कोहरा का तांडव। देश में सर्दी के तेवर बेहद तीखे बने हैं। ठंड से तो लोग पहले से ही परेशान थे अब कोहरे ने लोगों की परेशानी और बढ़ा दी है। न्यूनतम तापमान में लगातार गिरावट दर्ज की जा रही है। राजधानी दिल्ली में आज सुबह ठंड से कुछ राहत मिली। आज सुबह यहां का तापमान 7.1 डिग्री सेल्सियस दर्ज किया गया, जो सामान्य तापमान से एक डिग्री कम है। हालांकि दिल्ली-एनसीआर में तापमान में बढ़ोतरी के बाद भी ठिठुरन से लोगों को राहत नहीं मिली है। सुबह 4 बजे दिल्ली के IGI एयरपोर्ट पर विजिबिलिटी शून्य मापी गई जिसमें धीरे-धीरे सुधार हुआ लेकिन इसके चलते कई उड़ानें प्रभावित हुईं।

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3986: Popatlal Ki Date
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal hits it off with Anokhi, and both of them decide to go on a long drive together. Tapu Sena congratulates Popatlal, and all of them celebrate his success at the mall. Later, Popatlal tells his friends about the date, and he decides to take Sodhi's car for the long drive. Will things go according to Popatlal's plan?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3986, 20 Jan 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Mystery of Subhas Chandra Bose's Death | Gumnami Baba | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
In this video, we delve into the intriguing mystery surrounding the death of Subhas Chandra Bose, a key figure in India's fight for independence. After Japan's surrender in World War 2, Bose planned a secretive journey to the USSR, departing from Bangkok. Facing logistical challenges in war-torn Asia, his route included a complex flight plan with various stops. Tragically, the plane carrying Bose reportedly crashed in Taiwan. While some accounts state Bose perished in this crash, engulfed in flames, others suggest he survived and lived in hiding. The video explores various theories about his fate, including speculation that he was held captive in the USSR or lived incognito in India as 'Gumnami Baba'. This enduring mystery about Bose's death continues to fascinate and provoke debate, with numerous investigations and theories attempting to uncover the truth.

Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. snippet.title: Exclusive Look Of The Newly Built Ram Mandir & Ayodhya Airport | I Love My India | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Curly Tales has exclusive access to the newly built Ram Mandir &  Maharishi Valmiki Airport just before the launch. 
The Ram Mandir, set to be inaugurated on January 22nd, has preparations going on in full swing as around 4000 laborers are working on it around the clock. 
The temple is a testament to architectural marvel, constructed without the use of metal or concrete. Instead, a special rock imported from the Bansi Mountain in Rajasthan has been employed.
Along with that get a glimpse of Ayodhya’s four transformed lanes which are the - Bhaktipath, Janma Bhoomi Path, Ram Path & Dharma Path which are reconstructed on the basis of 4 vedas. 
You will also be amazed to see a new systematic way of Darshan for better crowd management that has been arranged by the government. 
Additionally, we give you an exclusive look at the Maharishi Valmiki International Airport, set to launch soon after being constructed in a record time of just 20 months. Inspired by the new Ram Mandir, the airport's walls are adorned with paintings depicting stories from the Ramayana. With the capacity to host about 10 lakh passengers annually, this airport is a remarkable addition to Ayodhya's infrastructure. 
So what are you waiting for,  book your tickets now as various modes of transportation have now been made available to visit Ram Lala.

snippet.title: Matka Opening Bracket | Varun tej | Karuna Kumar | Meenakshi | Nora Fatehi | GV Prakash |
snippet.description:
Watch MATKA Opening bracket here! 

#Matka is an upcoming Periodical Film starring Mega Prince Varun Tej in the Lead Role. Written and Directed by Karuna Kumar. It also co stars Meenakshi Chowdary, Nora Fatehi, Naveen Chandra and others. Music by GV Prakash Kumar, Cinematography by A Kishor Kumar and Proudly Produced on a massive scale by Dr. Vijender Reddy Teegala and Rajani Talluri under Vyra Entertainments in Association with SRT Entertainments.

The story which takes place between 1958-1982, is based on a real incident that shook the entire nation and the story is set in the backdrop of Vizag. The story spans 24 years. 

Cast: #VarunTej, #MeenakshiChowdary, #NoraFatehi, Naveen Chandra, Kannada Kishore, Ajay Ghosh, Mime Gopi, Roopalakshmi, Vijayrama Raju, Jagadeesh, Raj Thirandas.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3985 | 19 Jan 2024 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3985: Tapu Sena Helps Popatlal
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal gets separated from Tapu Sena at the mall, frantically searching for them. In the midst of his search, he comes across a girl who is unmarried just like him. Sensing an opportunity, Tapu Sena decides to assist Popatlal in making a positive impression on this girl.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3985, 19 Jan 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: VEG THALI | 15 Varieties of Veg Recipes | Huge South Indian Veg Thali Recipes Cooking In Village
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook 15 varieties of vegetarian recipes for the special Tamil day of the Pongal festival. We cook South Indian Veg thali recipes by cooking the following recipes: Rice, Sambar, Rasam, Mor, Payasam, Appalam, Vadai, Sweet Pongal, Potato fry, Lady Finger masala, Brinjal Masial, Raw banana Fry, Cabbage, Thandu Keerai Masiyal, and Pickle.

The taste is savory!

snippet.title: Choodu Nanna - Video Song | Yatra 2 | Mammootty | Jiiva | Mahi V Raghav | Santhosh Narayanan
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Telugu

Presenting the first single "Choodu Nanna" from 'Yatra 2' starring Mammootty, Jiiva & others. Directed by Mahi V Raghav, Music Composed by Santhosh Narayanan.

Song Credits:-
Lyrics : Bhaskarabhatla Ravi Kumar
Singers : Vijaynarain
Composed, Arranged and Programmed by Santhosh Narayanan
Additional Vocals : Santhosh Narayanan
Recorded by Santhosh Narayanan, Rupendar Venkatesh
Recorded at Future Tense Studios -  Chennai
Recording Engineer : Rupendar Venkatesh
Studio Assist : Jaba Raj
Mixed and Mastered by Santhosh Narayanan at Future Tense Studios
Musicians Coordinator : Meenakshi Santhosh

Movie Credits:-
Written & Directed by: Mahi V Raghav
Producer: Shiva Meka
Banners: Three Autumn Leaves, V Celluloid
Music Director: Santhosh Narayanan
DOP : Madhie
Editor : Shravan Katikaneni
Art Director: Selva Kumar
Cast :
Mammootty, Jiiva, Ketaki Narayan, Suzanne Bernert, Mahesh Manjrekar

Lyrics:-
Pallavi:
Choodu Naannaa...Choosthunnaavaa naannaa.. Needa leni nena veella dheema
yemitii enthatiii premaa.. 
Naa dhareto thochakunte 
 Nii vembadae memu antuu
Kadilaaru ento aa nammakam
Nenelaa odduku  cheradam...  Veellanelaa  odduku cherchadam

Charanam 1:
Inti peddhaa.. Kanumoosthey ainavaallu anadhale kadha. 
Nuvvu lekaa.. Prathi ooruu ooruu anadha avvadam yendayyaa..
  Nuvvu lekaa..... Nuvvu lekaa..... Nuvvu lekaa...
Idhi yenaaduu.. Jarigundadhayyaa.. Oo pedayya.. 
Indhari kannulu chimme kanniitinanthaa..
Thudavaalani vundhi kodukuga
Anduku avasaramaiyyee kondantha dhairyam naakivvu..

Charanam 2:
enthala abhimaaname kuripisthunnaro ee janam Anduke ee janmalo teerchesukuntaa ee runam Gadapaki prathi gadapaki nenavuthaa raksha thoranam  Maatapai untaanani chesthunnaa tholi santhakam
Needa leni nena veella dheema...
Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
 Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
 Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
     Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
